Kubernetes is a container orchestration platform.
Node installed as cluster
Container group of nodes(Pods)

Advanced concepts in k8s:
-------------------------
1. Muliple nodes    (multiple nodes as pod)
2. Auto healing     (without manual interruption the node stats automatically)
3. Auto scaling     (Replica set, Horizontal Pod Autoscaling(HPA))
4. Enterprise edition (contains Load Balancer, Firewall, API Gateway..)


#Difference between container and kubernetes
### Container                      | ###Kubernetes
-----------------------------------|-----------------------------
1. Container platform              | 1. Container orchestration platform
2. Single host                     | 2. Node installed as clusetr (Multiple nodes)
3. Ephemeral in nature(short life) | 3. Enterprise edition
                                   
